// Default eFLINT code that can be included in other eFLINT programs
// that are meant to be used through Akka. 
//
// It exports some functionality that is used by the Reasoner Actors,
// like setting the current time before each message is processed.

Fact actor
Fact reasoner Identified by actor

Fact hour Identified by Int
Fact current-hour Identified by hour

Act set-current-hour
  Actor reasoner
  Related to hour
  Obfuscates current-hour
  Creates current-hour()
